name: KNN
description: This notebook demonstrates the application of the K-Nearest Neighbors (KNN) algorithm, a simple and versatile machine learning method used for classification and regression tasks. KNN is a non-parametric, lazy-learning algorithm that makes predictions based on the majority class of k-nearest neighbors in the feature space.
